<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="adventure-n">adventure <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /əd'ventʃə(r)/    美 /əd'ventʃər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 冒险：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do you like adventure in your life?
生活中你喜欢冒险吗？</p><footer>人教⑥ – 5</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 冒险经历；奇遇：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The Adventures of Tom Sawyer
《汤姆·索亚历险记》</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Columbus’ discovery of the New World was an adventure.
哥伦布发现新大陆是一次奇遇。</p></div></div>